{"tid":2146846,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"基本發腐乳 不能打開瓶蓋","createTime":"2020-08-08T23:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T17:39:47.000Z","uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"04002b6279b9ac5dd71c7a36389dfd001593b9d5","tid":2146846,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T23:56:47.000Z","msg":"豆腐本是味道平淡之物，經過發酵後，其蛋白質轉化為更有利消化的氨基酸、煙酸及鈣等礦物質。<br />\n<br />\n黃豆麴或米麴釀製腐乳 ~ 把黃豆、米等蒸煮冷卻後製麴，豆腐鹽漬後混合黃豆麴熟成。二是接種毛黴菌法 ~ 將表面乾燥的豆腐接種毛黴菌培養成黴豆腐，再浸鹽水、加調味料熟成。<br />\n<br />\n發酵的速度視乎氣溫，夏天 2 ~ 3 個月完成，冬天時候或 4 ~ 5 個月，半年最好吃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n心得：釀製過程不能打開瓶蓋，也不用搖晃，是完全不能打開唷，否則讓雜菌進去會發霉的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRsZ4sWqdayXPP78WTNORA6WYJQ-BD_218yWA&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcRsZ4sWqdayXPP78WTNORA6WYJQ-BD_218yWA%26usqp%3DCAU&h=b5a87e96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90ec75f39b766bf0e831a525fd57126a8556c6b6","tid":2146846,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T08:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3064803dde158bb0c20b3d3a13c8ea44f276e6e6","tid":2146846,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:54:46.000Z","msg":"腐乳很好吃"},{"pid":"d4442da17a66a12c65488abb53e997903a2884a9","tid":2146846,"uid":125453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}